# Next.js 15 Latest Features & Performance Patterns

## Async Params Support (Next.js 15)
- **ALWAYS** handle params as async in dynamic routes:
  ```tsx
  export default async function Page({ 
    params 
  }: { 
    params: Promise<{ id: string }> 
  }) {
    const { id } = await params
    // Use id safely here
  }
  ```

